  "content": "hlight\">Five</span> Independent<br>\n    Reviewers\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"slide-subtitle\" style=\"font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 28px;\">\n    Each runs as a separate subagent. Own context window. Cites specific file:line references. Gives a verdict.\n  </div>\n  <!-- Standard 3 -->\n  <div style=\"font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent-blue); margin-bottom: 16px;\">Always Present</div>\n  <div style=\"display: flex; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n    <div style=\"flex: 1; background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-top: 4px solid var(--accent-blue); border-radius: 16px; padding: 24px;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 36px; margin-bottom: 8px;\">&#128187;</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 20px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent-blue);\">Senior SWE</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 16px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 8px; line-height: 1.6;\">Correctness, safety, race conditions, edge cases, performance</div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"flex: 1; background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-top: 4px solid var(--accent-amber); border-radius: 16px; padding: 24px;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 36px; margin-bottom: 8px;\">&#128203;</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 20px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent-amber);\">Product Manager</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 16px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 8px; line-height: 1.6;\">Goal alignment, scope creep, incomplete work, UX coherence</div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"flex: 1; background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-top: 4px solid var(--accent-green); border-radius: 16px; padding: 24px;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 36px; margin-bottom: 8px;\">&#128270;</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 20px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent-green);\">QA Engineer</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 16px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 8px; line-height: 1.6;\">Test coverage, failure modes, boundaries, regression risk</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>",
